{"tid":460212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佔中預計殺500人 　習近平否決梁振英建議","createTime":"2017-11-06T12:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-07T22:02:26.000Z","uid":141461,"like":13,"dislike":277,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"2231063a0fbbd3d0a256f3a3f10a7c08c86ec397","tid":460212,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T12:33:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.epochtimes.com.tw/upload/images/2014/09/30/107137_medium.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.epochtimes.com.tw%2Fupload%2Fimages%2F2014%2F09%2F30%2F107137_medium.jpg&h=b88b233d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 大雨澆不熄佔中民眾對自由民主的渴望，越晚越多人湧向各占領地點，有消息傳出香港特首梁振英計畫要鎮壓群眾，更預計殺500人。<br />\n<br />\n中共高層內幕消息29日指，梁振英和北京駐港最高機構「中聯辦」主任張曉明等28日向北京報告，提出請求開槍殺人，但計畫被中國國家主席習近平否決。<br />\n<br />\n30日再根據極可靠來源指出，梁振英、張曉明、劉延東、曾偉雄、張德江五人計畫提出鎮壓死亡人數「預算」500人，當天員警曾舉牌警告準備開槍，香港各大醫院也做了準備。"},{"pid":"b1cec40f6f31be174077e6b3dbbc698ca213e1cc","tid":460212,"uid":5253,"like":53,"dislike":84,"score":-31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T12:42:39.000Z","msg":"習爸爸係中國香港人既恩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e5cab5f2825332fd011afb1e6bab1f4f206441","tid":460212,"uid":79627,"like":84,"dislike":3,"score":81,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T12:45:48.000Z","msg":"Source 係大紀元？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebee8b0995e97de7416ba7f7b40e29ee983213dd","tid":460212,"uid":154385,"like":180,"dislike":3,"score":177,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T12:46:38.000Z","msg":"咁到有得吹<br />\n吹習近平係耶穌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a42967ba43d3cda204fd468b693aebbe79f3f24","tid":460212,"uid":154385,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T12:47:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁<span style=\"color: red;\">都</span>有得吹<br />\n吹習近平係耶穌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"711f9f53008d461064f165189816b2683bb0845d","ti