ji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f06fd3ed443fa48a7929c5ececd3210f508bd0a","tid":460212,"uid":22858,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:28:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>醫院咁多黃絲 你有咁既準備 佢地仲唔跑出黎講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果時有人影過醫院通告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依單新聞一兩年前已經睇過</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>醫院管理局最新公布（只有中文）<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n下稿代醫院管理局發出︰<br />\n<br />\n　　醫院管理局發言人作以下公布：<br />\n<br />\n　　由於政府總部集會關係，本局預計有大量傷者需要送院接受治療。市民如有需要到港島區三間急症室（瑪麗醫院、律敦治及鄧肇堅醫院、東區尤德夫人那打素醫院）求診，輪候時間有機會較平日長，敬請耐心等候。<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n２０１４年９月２８日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間１８時４５分</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201409/28/P201409280831.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201409%2F28%2FP201409280831.htm&d=AzlJ5qUn41umfvhC4ygFVviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=7e5a8e0f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201409/28/P201409280831.htm</a></span>"},{"pid":"6675b45ea1e518d353b68ff39d172578bd7cba5f","tid":460212,"uid":22858,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:28:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一起樓主底原來係跑跑卡丁車好玩</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><ins>細字濃縮試用版</ins><br />\n經crosscheck多個post，確信五毛名單臚列如下：三色貓、法國佬巫斯義、極右派政治家、群龍共舞、優美開始、JR、RedBaron、Gladiclus、D_Wade、dewi、newlife、bbchu、十卜Ching、侵B、吾系甘開心牙、返六日唔撚易、毛澤東<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\